user.biography:
Creating beautiful, clean spaces, one machine washable rug at a time... and doormats, too!
We currently ship to 🇺🇸, 🇨🇦 & 🇬🇧
#JAxRuggable rugs👇

node.text:
You may not know this, but all of our rug patterns are created in-house by a team of textile designers! They make designs with inspiration from all over the world.

Now, we’re giving you a rare peek inside their process with our series, Behind the Design. Every week a designer will take over to share how they created some of our most loved rugs. Tune into our Stories every Saturday for Behind the Design! 🎨✨
